{"tid":1240340,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[林鄭似我]P街...做錯事","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:04:59.000Z","uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1517cd59542e9b09e399eec40da373d1b09ffc","tid":1240340,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"同一件事錯完一次又一次...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(重唔係7婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n返工做錯其實無可避免...<br />\n唔好錯太甘同補返鑊其實就算...<br />\n慘在去補又補唔晒...但明明係可以補得晒...重花咗額外唔少功夫同力氣去補...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後又柒過...<br />\n屌...好撚嬲自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老闆唔係度...但相信明天返到公司少不免被屌...<br />\n又冇得引咎辭職...<br />\n十足7婆...係冇40萬一個月...(1/10都冇)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26f89844cf836f0d3067573a17eb43798e6c0c7","tid":1240340,"uid":104544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"［告解］<br />\n我最近都係呀<br />\n我又唔識講大話果類，呢兩日番工好心虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108306f85ff41ea10c80176b11a356be2fa50c54","tid":1240340,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f26f89844cf836f0d3067573a17eb43798e6c0c7","tid":1240340,"uid":104544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"［告解］<br />\n我最近都係呀<br />\n我又唔識講大話果類，呢兩日番工好心虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"希望你成功~<br />\n但講真...東窗事發的話好多時重大鑊過自爆...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas